    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is offset by direct bench-test confirmation of all three QoIs within pre-established acceptance bounds (E/uval < 1.96; percentage difference < 10%). Overall credibility is sufficient to support regulatory submission of the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw FEA framework.",
